  "detailed_description": "<i>Castillo Shattered Mirrors</i> is a first-person shooter that combines the frantic shooting of retro FPS games with the fun exploration of the collect-a-thons that ruled the late 90s.<br><br>Your supernatural investigation goes a bit too far when you come across Dracula's castle and discover his dimension-hopping plan of dimensional domination. Battle your way through different apocalyptic dimensions, fighting hordes of monsters and finding crystal shards. Collect shards to open up new areas to Dracula's castle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870970/extras/8838f934569ff7da3d688897fef8cff7.poster.avif?t=1717745165\" width=604 height=55 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870970/extras/8838f934569ff7da3d688897fef8cff7.webm?t=1717745165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2>- <strong>Open-ended hub world</strong>, explore Dracula's castle and open up portals to shattered dimensions.<br>- <strong>Fast-paced action</strong>, fight a vast array of different enemies<br>- <strong>11 weapons</strong>, kill monsters with different unique weapons throughout your dangerous journey.<br>- <strong>Over 100 different levels</strong>, filled with action-packed combat and interesting story.<br>- <strong>13 different worlds to explore</strong>, recover crystal shards in space stations, abandoned snow research bases, spooky forests, and more<br>- <strong>Choose which levels to play in any order</strong>, you have the freedom to pick from multiple worlds to complete in the hub world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870970/extras/95dd85e4093f4d9c3a1594534d4ba1df.poster.avif?t=1717745165\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870970/extras/95dd85e4093f4d9c3a1594534d4ba1df.webm?t=1717745165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870970/extras/95dd85e4093f4d9c3a1594534d4ba1df.mp4?t=1717745165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870970/extras/d55e45d1baf9e8ec9217011b6791fdfc.poster.avif?t=1717745165\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870970/extras/d55e45d1baf9e8ec9217011b6791fdfc.webm?t=1717745165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870970/extras/d55e45d1baf9e8ec9217011b6791fdfc.mp4?t=1717745165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<i>Castillo Shattered Mirrors</i> is a first-person shooter that combines the frantic shooting of retro FPS games with the fun exploration of the collect-a-thons that ruled the late 90s.<br><br>Your supernatural investigation goes a bit too far when you come across Dracula's castle and discover his dimension-hopping plan of dimensional domination. Battle your way through different apocalyptic dimensions, fighting hordes of monsters and finding crystal shards. Collect shards to open up new areas to Dracula's castle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870970/extras/8838f934569ff7da3d688897fef8cff7.poster.avif?t=1717745165\" width=604 height=55 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870970/extras/8838f934569ff7da3d688897fef8cff7.webm?t=1717745165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2>- <strong>Open-ended hub world</strong>, explore Dracula's castle and open up portals to shattered dimensions.<br>- <strong>Fast-paced action</strong>, fight a vast array of different enemies<br>- <strong>11 weapons</strong>, kill monsters with different unique weapons throughout your dangerous journey.<br>- <strong>Over 100 different levels</strong>, filled with action-packed combat and interesting story.<br>- <strong>13 different worlds to explore</strong>, recover crystal shards in space stations, abandoned snow research bases, spooky forests, and more<br>- <strong>Choose which levels to play in any order</strong>, you have the freedom to pick from multiple worlds to complete in the hub world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870970/extras/95dd85e4093f4d9c3a1594534d4ba1df.poster.avif?t=